code: @Override public boolean canBuild(FormattingOptions formattingOptions) {     return formattingOptions.getClazz().isEnum(). }

@Override public Format<?> build(FormattingOptions formattingOptions) {     @SuppressWarnings({ "rawtypes", "unchecked" })     EnumFormat enumFormat = new EnumFormat(formattingOptions.getClazz()).     return enumFormat. }
public String format(final T object) throws Exception {     return object.name(). }
public T parse(final String string) throws Exception {     return Enum.valueOf(clazz, string). }
